  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/7800/extras/cca1e9fef613611c58b9ca7cb97b21be.avif?t=1680629661\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be the Zombie. Kick A** and Take Brains</h2>It’s 1959 and the city of Punchbowl, PA, is a beacon of progress and ideal living. Show the living that law and order are no match for a dead man on a mission. Your boyfriend’s back Maggie, and Punchbowl is gonna be in trouble!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/7800/extras/f21b736baadd208c154a8f299a45c86a.avif?t=1680629661\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Eat Brains</h2> Chomp on the living and replenish your bodily arsenal of: zombie sputum, gut grenades, and the stunning unholy flatulence<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/7800/extras/18556ae80becd9ac476581a1da34df24.avif?t=1680629661\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Possess Punchbowl’s Population</h2> Clamp your severed hand to a barbershop quartet singer’s head and raygun away<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/7800/extras/a52b0db0dd32b0cb62bce0749160c513.avif?t=1680629661\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Zombie Horde</h2> Convert your enemies into undead allies & lead a zombie assault on the living<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/7800/extras/dfb9b05c5bed05d9c32da6d4c1116f27.avif?t=1680629661\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring Civilization to its Knees</h2> Show the retro-futuristic city of Punchbowl, PA that they can’t escape the past<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/7800/extras/f8dfd15076a56358abcb3a132cd66d56.avif?t=1680629661\" width=616 height=346 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stubbs and Chill</h2> Invite a friend to play as Grubbs for classic couch cooperative hijinks. (Friend not included)",
